title: Instant Reaction: Boston Wins Game 7 and Heat vs. Celtics Preview
description:
Kevin O'Connor and Logan Murdock hop on right after Celtics-Raptors Game 7 to share their instant reactions (00:11) as well as a very early preview of the Eastern Conference Finals (13:10). Plus, quick thoughts on the Nuggets surviving elimination against the Clippers (17:33).
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Kevin O'Connor
